      "data": {
        "title": "Choosing The Artifact",
        "body": "Use this rule of thumb:\n\n- if you need a reusable kind of node, make a node class\n- if you need a reusable kind of relationship, make an edge class\n- if you need a reusable graph arrangement, make a template\n\nBridges help distribute those things. They are support machinery, not the headline artifact.",
        "_classBinding": {
